data.description: This 3-bedroom/1-bath ranch home has been totally renovated and is move-in ready! You’ll love the cheerful kitchen with brand new cabinets/counters and a door that leads to the fenced backyard. Just off the kitchen is the spacious formal dining room,  laundry room with plenty of space for storage and a new remodeled full bathroom. The living room features a large set of windows letting in lots of natural daylight. Many other updates/upgrades include a new metal roof, new soffit and fascia, all new windows, new steps front and back, updated electric, updated plumbing, new vinyl plank flooring (water resistant), new 95% efficient gas furnace and new energy efficient hot water tank. Don’t wait, call to schedule your showing today!
